Popular Moja Love show Uyajola 9/9 has been rocked by fake social media accounts. This is after a fake Twitter account which has over 100 000 followers already has been posing as the official Twitter account of the highly popular show. ALSO READ: REFILWE NAMED BEST OF BEST! In a statement Moja Love slammed the fake social media accounts and said they do not condone any form of discrimination on the basis of race, gender, sexual orientation, religion and culture. This is due to the fact that the Twitter account which is in question has been sending out tweets which were homophobic and some slightly racist. One of the tweets said: "The first sign that your man likes other men is if he asks for anal." READ MOJA LOVE'S STATEMENT BELOW:  